These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: iris, amaryllis, daisy, zinnia
Food: radish, eggplant, tomato, strawberry
1. Flower:iris is on the right of Food:tomato##1
2. Food:strawberry is on the far left##1
3. Food:tomato is between Food:eggplant and Flower:amaryllis##2
4. Flower:zinnia is on the far left##1
5. Flower:daisy is between Flower:amaryllis and Flower:iris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | zinnia         | amaryllis   | daisy | iris       |
| Food      | strawberry | radish | tomato   | eggplant |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Game: whist, canasta, poker, snooker
City: hamburg, venice, paris, new-york
1. City:new-york is between Game:poker and City:venice##2
2. Game:snooker is on the far right##1
3. City:paris is on the right of City:hamburg##1
4. Game:whist is on the left of City:hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | canasta | whist | poker | snooker |
| City   | venice    | new-york   | hamburg | paris       |

