2. Game:snooker is between Game:bridge and Flower:lily##2
3. Game:bridge is on the far left##1
4. Game:domino is on the left of Flower:orchid##1
5. Flower:lily == Game:domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Flower          | daisy    | tulip | lily   | orchid  |
| Game   | bridge | snooker   | domino | go |

