3. Music-Genre:country is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the far right##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Game:backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
